result.execSummary:
One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Levante Terelle Reed is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

On one or more other charges, Levante Terelle Reed was found not guilty. These charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Levante Terelle Reed is presumed innocent of the not guilty charges.
